[I] An RFC 3986 URI parsing library

[T] Uriparser is a strictly RFC 3986 compliant URI parsing library. It is
[T] cross-platform, fast, and supports Unicode.

[U] https://uriparser.sourceforge.net/

[A] Sebastian Pipping <webmaster@hartwork.org>
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

